data.description: Located close to the beach and Langley AFB, this lovely home has a bright and open floor plan and a great back yard with privacy fence and storage shed! The open flow of the home is great for entertaining; the family room features a wood fireplace and plenty of room for seating, the EIK includes a large area for table and chairs and also has a counter where you can fit a row of stools. The lovely dining room and formal living room/office flow together for a very flexible space with lots of possibilities. The primary suite includes double closet, and the home offers extended driveway space.
